se.miun.itm.input.model.mapping

Class Framework.DocumentWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.miun.itm.input.model.mapping.Framework.DocumentWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Framework.DocumentWrapper>
    Enclosing class:
    Framework

    private static class Framework.DocumentWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Framework.DocumentWrapper>
    A DocumentWrapper wraps a code-mapping document in order to provide references to the framework to which it belongs and to the next and previous element in the framework's linked sequence of DocumentWrapper:s. In addition, DocumentWrapper:s are Comparable.
